00:00:31.600 --> 00:00:35.740
Parse a JSON payload into separate fields for analysis,

00:00:35.740 --> 00:00:39.630
join two streaming DataFrames from different data sources,

00:00:39.630 --> 00:00:45.000
and write a streaming DataFrame to Kafka with aggregated data.

